descriptionHtml:
A replacer for the standalone \"Field Mage Outfit CBBEv3 by Echo 1162\" fit to the ADEC body.

YOU NEED THE ORIGINAL FILES. ALL THIS CONTAINS IS NEW ADEC MESHES.

All credit goes to Echo for making these to begin with, all I did was refit them. As well as Acdale, for his amazing ADEC body. You will need a physics skeleton, since it has bouncies.

No I won\'t fit to any other bodies. No I won\'t do anything with it. If you think you can improve it you\'re welcome to it.

Long live ADEC!
author: Abusive Echo 1162
